        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Dorsal habitus (a), female pronotum (b–e) and male genital segment with parameres (f–h) of Loricula pilosella Miyamoto (a,b,f), L. nikko sp. nov. (d). L. miyamotoi sp. nov. (c,g) L. yakushima sp. nov. (e, h) Figures (a) and (f) redrawn from Miyamoto (1965)." ;
